<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>授权申请</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,minimum-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
    <meta http-equiv="pragma" content="no-cache">
    <meta http-equiv="cache-control" content="no-cache">
    <meta http-equiv="expires" content="0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/checkOthers.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/common.css">
    <script type="text/javascript" src="js/jquery-1.11.3.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="js/common.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="libs/layui/layui.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="js/checkOthers.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        ! function () {
            var html = document.documentElement;
            var hWidth = html.getBoundingClientRect().width;
            html.style.fontSize = hWidth / 15 + 'px';
        }();
    </script>
</head>

<body>
    <div id="header">
    </div>
    <div class="licensedContent">
        <div class="licensedContentTitle">
            <img src="images/licensedContent-icon.png" alt="">
            <h2> 将授权的内容包括</h2>
        </div>
        <ul class="clearfix">
            <li>
                <img src="images/a1.png" alt="">
                <p>身份信息核验</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <img src="images/a6.png" alt="">
                <p>职业资格核验</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <img src="images/a7.png" alt="">
                <p>公共治安信息核验</p>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="lineWrap">
            <div class="line"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="price clearfix">
            <span>价格：6元</span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="basicWrap">
        <div class="basic">
            <span class="msg-authorize active">短信授权</span>
            <span class="scan-authorize">扫码授权</span>
        </div>
        <div id="basicFormDiv">
            <form id="deForm" class="basicForm  clearfix">
                <label for="resumeName">
                    <i class="icon1"></i>
                    <span>姓名</span>
                    <input id="verifyName" type="text" name="verifyName" data-attribute="请填写正确的姓名" placeholder="请输入候选人姓名" maxlength="20">
                </label>
                <br>
                <label for="resumeMobile">
                    <i class="icon2"></i>
                    <span class="inpTel">联系方式</span>
                    <input id="verifyMobile" type="text" name="verifyMobile" data-attribute="请填写正确的联系方式" placeholder="请填写候选人手机号" maxlength="11">
                </label>
                <br>
                <button type="button" class="nextStep">申请授权</button>
            </form>
        </div>
        <div id="qrCodeDiv" class="qrCode active">
            <img src="images/code.png" alt="">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>提示：</p>
        <p>1、候选人同意授权后，才能对齐进行核验</p>
        <p>候选人授权后，直接通过【报告】tab进行付款查看报告</p>
    </div>
    <!--遮罩-->
    <div class="zhezhao"></div>
    <div id="loading" class="loader-inner line-scale">
        <div></div>
        <div></div>
        <div></div>
        <div></div>
        <div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="footerTab">
       <p>
			<img src="images/index_sel.png" alt=""> 
			<span class="active"><a href="index.html">首页</a></span>
		</p>
		<p>
			<img src="images/report_pre.png" alt=""> 
			<span><a href="reportList.html">报告</a></span>
		</p>
		<p>
			<img src="images/my-pre.png" alt=""> 
			<span><a href="personal.html">我的</a></span>
		</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>